# Reference only — set these in EB Console > Configuration > Software > Environment properties.
# Do NOT commit real secret values to this file.
#
# Required:
#   DB_URL, DB_USER, DB_PASS
#   JWT_SECRET (min 32 bytes)
#   RAZORPAY_KEY_ID, RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET
#   MAIL_USERNAME, MAIL_PASSWORD
#   SHIPROCKET_EMAIL, SHIPROCKET_PASSWORD
#   ALLOWED_ORIGINS, FRONTEND_URL
#
# Optional:
#   RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET
#   ADMIN_INITIAL_PASSWORD (first deploy only)
#   AWS_S3_BUCKET, AWS_S3_REGION
#
# Use IAM instance profile for S3 — leave AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID and AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY empty.
